cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.CY 

The paper proposes a private SGD algorithm for scalable analytics systems, which involves machine learning (ML) and database (DB) technologies. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves analysis of the $L_2$-sensitivity of SGD, which is related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CY).
